---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
  metadata={{
    title: 'TapRebook Modules — Pick what fits your workflow',
    description:
      'Choose modules by outcome: clinics, labs, pharma, dental labs, hospitality, education, and restaurants. Each solves a different problem and can be used alone or together.',
  }}
>
  <!-- HERO with image -->
  <section class="relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-20 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_.85fr] items-center">
      <!-- Left copy -->
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Modules</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700/90 max-w-3xl">
          Choose the module that matches your workflow. Each solves a different problem and can run on its own,
          or alongside others under one brand—shared data, consistent messaging.
        </p>

        <!-- Quick “help me choose” -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Help me choose</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/about/">How TapRebook works</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: visual -->
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white/55 ring-1 ring-white/40 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
        <img
          src="/images/AI_modules.png"
          alt="TapRebook modules overview: Reception, Labs, Pharma, DentalLab, Stay, Campus, Queue"
          class="block w-full h-full object-cover"
          width="1600"
          height="1000"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
          sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 520px, 90vw"
        />
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-white/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HEALTHCARE -->
  <section class="py-10 border-t border-white/20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Healthcare</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700/90">
            Reception, Labs, Pharma, and DentalLab cover the core patient journey—each module addresses a distinct need.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <!-- Reception -->
        <a href="/modules/reception/" class="group rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur hover:opacity-95 transition">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/80">Clinic front desk</div>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-lg">Reception</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Confirmations, reminders, running-late handling, rescheduling, and no-show recovery.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600/80">Outcome: fewer no-shows, less phone tag.</div>
        </a>

        <!-- Labs -->
        <a href="/modules/labs/" class="group rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur hover:opacity-95 transition">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/80">Diagnostics & radiology</div>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-lg">Labs</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Prep instructions, nudges, status updates (sample/scan/report), and results share.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600/80">Outcome: fewer prep errors, smoother visits.</div>
        </a>

        <!-- Pharma -->
        <a href="/modules/pharma/" class="group rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur hover:opacity-95 transition">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/80">Pharmacy & adherence</div>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-lg">Pharma</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Refill nudges, chronic-care schedules, dosage checks, and escalation to staff.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600/80">Outcome: fewer lapses in medication.</div>
        </a>

        <!-- DentalLab -->
        <a href="/modules/dentallab/" class="group rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur hover:opacity-95 transition">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/80">Dentist ↔ lab ops</div>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-lg">DentalLab</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Pickups, photo approvals, and status visibility—impression received → ready → delivered.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600/80">Outcome: streamlined case handoffs.</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOSPITALITY -->
  <section class="py-10 border-t border-white/20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Hospitality</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700/90">
            Reduce calls and walk-aways with proactive WhatsApp flows for guest messaging and waitlists.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Stay -->
        <a href="/modules/stay/" class="group rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur hover:opacity-95 transition">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/80">Homestays & houseboats</div>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-lg">Stay</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Pre-arrival info, check-in nudges, upsells, and post-stay reviews—on WhatsApp.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600/80">Outcome: happier guests, fewer calls.</div>
        </a>

        <!-- Queue -->
        <a href="/modules/queue/" class="group rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur hover:opacity-95 transition">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/80">Restaurants</div>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-lg">Queue</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Join via QR, live position updates, preorders, and table-ready alerts.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600/80">Outcome: faster turns, fewer walk-aways.</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EDUCATION -->
  <section class="py-10 border-t border-white/20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Education</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700/90">
            Parent communications made reliable—broadcasts, acknowledgements, fees, events, and audits.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Campus -->
        <a href="/modules/campus/" class="group rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur hover:opacity-95 transition">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/80">Schools & coaching</div>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-lg">Campus</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Notices, fees, attendance, trips, and two-way updates—with escalation to staff.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600/80">Outcome: fewer calls, clearer records.</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW THEY FIT TOGETHER -->
  <section class="py-12 border-t border-white/20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center">Use one—or combine a few</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-center text-slate-700/90">
        Each module is purpose-built. Many teams start with one high-impact area, then add another when it makes sense.
        Workflows stay consistent and data stays connected.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Shared building blocks</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Buttons, replies, tags, and KPIs behave the same way across modules—less retraining.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Brand-consistent</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Templates share tone, style, and languages—patients/guests see one brand.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 backdrop-blur">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Measurable outcomes</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700/90">
            Track completions, drop-offs, and exceptions; escalate edge cases to staff.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 md:flex items-center justify-between">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Not sure which module fits?</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700/90">
          Tell us your goal and context—we’ll recommend a setup in 10 minutes.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 flex gap-3">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Book a demo</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href={`https://wa.me/${import.meta.env.PUBLIC_WA_NUMBER}`}>WhatsApp us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>


